{"tid":879832,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Chef Lemon出漢堡包！謝霆鋒設計安格斯牛肉肉醬煎蛋包","createTime":"2018-10-28T09:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T18:26:30.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9556c5b7159609c71a7f6199f31171cf437f30e0","tid":879832,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T09:55:51.000Z","msg":"說到謝霆鋒，相對於其歌手印象，不少人可能對其煮食的印象更為深刻，近年以「鋒味」作招牌推出一系列食品及電視節目，今次與麥當勞合作，推出「鋒味」The Signature Collection及其他食品，分兩期推出。<br />\n<br />\n系列食品以肉醬煎蛋飯及洋葱豬扒飯為主打，靈感源於謝霆鋒自幼在片場拍戲時經常吃到的飯盒，不過材料大升級，以澳洲及烏拉圭的130g安格斯牛肉烹調，再配上煎蛋及秘製肉醬，咬落漢堡牛味算特出，但味道未算太特別，反而洋葱吉列豬扒包味道不錯，豬扒厚身有咬口，配上炒洋葱及炸洋葱，更富口感。<br />\n<br />\n另外亦有一些港式shake shake調味粉及曲奇奶茶雪糕等，想要一嘗麥當勞的The Signature Collection或是鋒味食物，現在只要去麥當勞就能一試。<br />\n<br />\n採訪、攝影：范名雅<br />\n<br />\n「麥當勞X鋒味」The Signature Collection<br />\n供應日期：<br />\n第一期10月26日起<br />\n第二期11月20日起<br />\n供應時間：早上11時後<br />\n供應地點：全線麥當勞（長洲、沙田馬場及跑馬地馬場除外；海洋公園只供應鋒味橙汁雜飲及鋒味曲奇奶茶麥旋風）<br />\n註﹕漢堡包單點$29起，套餐$39起<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181026/large/1540526302_fd51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181026%2Flarge%2F1540526302_fd51.jpg&h=3c1f16ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181026/large/1540526301_3a40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181026%2Flarge%2F1540526301_3a40.jpg&h=b5c4d4de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181026/large/1540526304_520e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181026%2Flarge%2F1540526304_520e.jpg&h=52573c6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181026/large/1540526306_59e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181026%2Flarge%2